Titolo: Assault Suit Leynos 2

Anno: 1997

Descrizione: Assault Suit Leynos 2 is a 1997 Japanese run and gun video game developed by NCS for the Sega Saturn. It is a direct sequel to Assault Suit Leynos, for the Mega Drive and is the third title in the Assault Suits series. It is a side-scrolling mecha shooting game set in the future.